# Database Guidelines

- Uses Prisma ORM with Neondb for all database operations
- Database client is configured in [lib/prisma.js](mdc:lib/prisma.js)
- Schema and migrations are in the `prisma/` directory
- Always use the Prisma client for database access
- Follow established query patterns and robust error handling
- All SeoBot articles must be stored and indexed for SEO optimization
